escription2.png?t=1726777824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If you make a mistake at any point in the game, you always have the option of <strong>unlimited UNDOs</strong> or clearing the board entirely.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/description3.png?t=1726777824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The pre-generated levels not to your liking? No problem! Use the custom level generator and setup the game grid with the size and difficulty of your choosing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/extras/description5.png?t=1726777824\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> 150 pre-generated levels ranging from easy (6x6 grid) to difficult (20x20 grid)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> A custom level generator allowing you to choose any difficulty you want</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Minimalist design</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Relaxing background music</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unlimited UNDO options if you make a mistake</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dark Mode</p></li></ul>","developers":["Kouzii"],"genres":[{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3176800/header.jpg?t=1726777824","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257051217,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257051217/movie480.mp4?t=1725121181","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257051217/movie_max.mp4?t=1725121181"},"name":"Gridlink Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steam